5 of its business. The sales tax shall apply to the purchase of motor
6 fuel or diesel fuel in Oklahoma by a common carrier by rail when
7 such motor fuel is purchased for fueling, within this state, of any
8 locomotive or other motorized flanged wheel equipment;
