7 employees, as certified by the Oklahoma Employment Security
8 Commission, upon completion of the facility. In order to qualify
9 for the exemption provided for by this paragraph, the cost of the
10 items purchased by the qualified aircraft maintenance or
11 manufacturing facility shall equal or exceed the sum of Two Million
12 Dollars ($2,000,000.00) As used in this paragraph, “qualified
13 aircraft maintenance facility” means a facility operated by an air
14 common carrier including one or more component overhaul support
