17 thousand full-time-equivalent employees in the preceding year as
18 certified by the Oklahoma Employment Security Commission and which
19 is primarily related to the fabrication, repair, alteration,
20 modification, refurbishing, maintenance, building, or rebuilding of
21 commercial aircraft or aircraft parts used in air common carriage.
